text.tspan: This is a very simple mod that opens the door to very complex things.
URL Post Wand reports target block data.
Using the URL Config Wand on Signs, Chests, Barrels,
Comparators, Sculk and Light Sensors, Lecterns
Chests, Trapped Chests, and Barrels report full inventory contents when changed
Signs and Hanging Signs report front and back text
Sculk sensors transmit frequency, phase, and power level
Daylight sensors transmit power and invert status
"device": block, wand, chest, barrel, lectern, signs
All URLium devices transmit these fields in addition to device-specific data:
URLium transmits redstone and block information over HTTP(S) to webservers.
